wordpressPost.title: Kissybook
wordpressPost.content: The Kissybook is a colaborative art project that seems like a really cool idea, which is why I drew this cute little bunny in hopes of being included in the book. We'll see how it goes, I'll be sure to buy a copy, or a few, if I get in.
